 substantially reduced. This feature\nsuggests that free exciton can be trapped in disordered potential wells to form\na localized exciton and therefore offers a route toward novel optical\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2016 08:38:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-20"}
