, we demonstrate the\nimpact of traffic load and femto access points density on the performance of\nCCUs/CEUs under CSA and SSA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2016 11:32:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2017 11:16:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-10"}
