ls along with\na very interesting magnetic sensitivity in the wings of the linear polarization\nprofiles. We also show that the weak-field approximation has to be used with\ncaution when PRD effects are considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2016 13:38:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-22"}
