nerator of null infinity. Our results are in perfect\nagreement with the usual power-law decay discussed in previous work. This\narticle also contains a detailed analysis for the asymptotic behavior and\nregularity of the lapse, conformal factor, extrinsic curvature and the\nMisner-Sharp mass function along constant mean curvature slices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2016 14:56:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2017 22:29:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
